Social Development Minister Lindiwe Zulu briefs the media on the department’s response to COVID-19. The WhatsApp and related electronic application options will be demonstrated by the Minister at the launch. The social development portfolio, comprised of the Department of Social Development, the National Development Agency and the South African Social Security Agency (SASSA), says  the grant has passed the final stage of development and is ready for implementation. Minister Zulu presented a comprehensive report on the matter to the National Coordinating Council on Sunday. 